content.p: The Counselling Service is not an emergency service. We do not run an out of hours service. If you need urgent help, please contact: If you are on campus, you can contact Security in an emergency on 0115 95 18888. Security Control and Emergencies are in operation 24 hours, 7 days a week. If you are off campus in an emergency call 999. The Orchards University Park Nottingham, NG7 2RD telephone: +44 (0)115 951 3695 email: counselling.service@nottingham.ac.uk
